appetite /ˈæpɪˌtaɪt/

(appetites) 

1. N-VAR Your appetite is your desire to eat. 胃口 

例： He has a healthy appetite. 他有健康的胃口。 

2. N-COUNT Someone's appetite for something is their strong desire for it. 欲望 

例： ...his appetite for success. …他的成功欲望。

